# Default Avatar Placeholder

This folder contains default avatar images for users who haven't uploaded their own profile pictures.

## Included Files
- `default-user.png` - Generic user avatar
- `default-male.png` - Male-oriented default avatar (optional)
- `default-female.png` - Female-oriented default avatar (optional)
- `default-neutral.png` - Gender-neutral default avatar

## Usage
Reference these images when user profile pictures are not available:

```typescript
getAvatarUrl(user: User): string {
  return user.profilePicture || 'assets/images/avatars/default-user.png';
}
```
